constructor.description: Initializes the contract with a logic address and initialization data.

fallback.description: Fallback function that allows the contract to receive Ether.

receive.description: Receive function that allows the contract to receive Ether.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin of the contract is changed.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon address is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the implementation address is upgraded.
